            </div>
            <h3 data-i18n="s01.c3.h3">Know the right question to ask</h3>
            <p data-i18n="s01.c3.p">
              kuku picks up on context and suggests follow-up prompts to keep your thinking moving.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lp-feat-viz">
            <div
